590
00:48:26,100 --> 00:48:27,100
<font color="yellow">Tidur saja lagi.</font>

591
00:48:27,500 --> 00:48:29,660
<font color="yellow">Kenapa baru bangun
lalu langsung mengusirku?</font>

592
00:48:29,660 --> 00:48:31,570
<font color="yellow">Nanti aku bayar, pergilah.</font>

593
00:48:32,330 --> 00:48:33,670
<font color="yellow">Aku harus ke sekolah.</font>

594
00:48:34,030 --> 00:48:35,620
<font color="yellow">Pergi saja, jangan pedulikan aku!</font>

595
00:48:35,620 --> 00:48:38,370
<font color="yellow">Aku buat kimci, bersih-bersih dulu,
baru aku pergi.</font>

596
00:48:39,430 --> 00:48:40,650
<font color="yellow">Aku tidak mau.</font>

597
00:48:40,650 --> 00:48:42,500
<font color="yellow">Aku tak butuh bantuanmu.</font>

598
00:48:43,500 --> 00:48:45,530
<font color="yellow">Kenapa kau mengeluh terus?</font>

599
00:48:46,530 --> 00:48:49,390
<font color="yellow">Kau tak punya anak, suamimu kaya.</font>

600
00:48:49,390 --> 00:48:50,690
<font color="yellow">Kau lulusan sarjana.</font>

601
00:48:50,690 --> 00:48:52,120
<font color="yellow">Apa aku ini pembantumu?</font>

602
00:48:52,120 --> 00:48:54,250
<font color="yellow">Pembantu saja diperlakukan
dengan baik.</font>

603
00:48:54,250 --> 00:48:58,490
<font color="yellow">Kau selalu tidur tiap kali
aku datang!</font>

604
00:48:58,490 --> 00:48:59,860
<font color="yellow">Aku tak pernah bisa melihatmu!</font>

605
00:48:59,860 --> 00:49:01,990
<font color="yellow">Ini pertemuan pertama kita
setelah satu bulan...,</font>

606
00:49:01,990 --> 00:49:04,430
<font color="yellow">...tapi kau bilang mau membayarku
dan menyuruhku pergi?</font>

607
00:49:06,830 --> 00:49:08,430
<font color="yellow">Berisik, pergilah.</font>

608
00:49:09,600 --> 00:49:13,100
<font color="yellow">Aku pergi, kau cegah pun aku tetap pergi.
Siapa juga yang mau disini?</font>

609
00:49:19,130 --> 00:49:20,590
<font color="yellow">Cepat pergi!</font>

610
00:49:20,590 --> 00:49:21,960
<font color="yellow">Aku mau beres-beres dulu!</font>

611
00:49:21,960 --> 00:49:23,000
<font color="yellow">Nih, aku sudah beres-beres!</font>

612
00:50:51,900 --> 00:50:54,090
<font color="yellow">Ibu, ini Soo Young.
Kenapa belum datang?</font>

613
00:50:54,090 --> 00:50:55,320
<font color="yellow">Tidak bersih-bersih?</font>

614
00:50:55,320 --> 00:50:58,610
<font color="yellow">Aku sibuk siap-siap kerja,
rumah sangat berantakan.</font>

615
00:50:58,610 --> 00:51:00,090
<font color="yellow">Kalau tidak datang, ya sudah.</font>

616
00:51:00,090 --> 00:51:02,930
<font color="yellow">Kau tak pernah tepat waktu,
menyebalkan.</font>

617
00:51:03,330 --> 00:51:04,570
<font color="yellow">Datanglah minggu depan.</font>

618
00:51:16,330 --> 00:51:17,400
<font color="yellow">Ibu?</font>

619
00:51:18,970 --> 00:51:22,200
<font color="yellow">Ah, Perawat.</font>

620
00:51:25,630 --> 00:51:26,870
<font color="yellow">Apa Ibu...</font>

621
00:51:29,730 --> 00:51:31,230
<font color="yellow">...seburuk itu?</font>

622
00:51:32,000 --> 00:51:35,970
<font color="yellow">Sepertinya tak bisa bertahan lama.</font>

623
00:51:36,530 --> 00:51:38,730
<font color="yellow">Dia baru saja kembali dari
rumah sakit.</font>

624
00:51:40,370 --> 00:51:43,420
<font color="yellow">Tadinya mau kubungi kemarin
saat dia sedang kritis...,</font>

625
00:51:43,420 --> 00:51:46,370
<font color="yellow">...tapi itu juga pasti
tak banyak membantu.</font>

626
00:51:47,130 --> 00:51:48,800
<font color="yellow">Jadi kami sendiri yang mengawasinya.</font>

627
00:51:49,700 --> 00:51:51,720
<font color="yellow">Sebaiknya kau datang...</font>

628
00:51:51,720 --> 00:51:54,230
<font color="yellow">...mumpung dia masih
bisa mengenalimu.</font>

629
00:51:55,430 --> 00:52:00,870
<font color="yellow">Dokter memperkirakan tidak
sampai satu bulan.</font>

630
00:52:02,870 --> 00:52:04,370
<font color="yellow">Baiklah.</font>

631
00:52:05,870 --> 00:52:07,500
<font color="yellow">Aku akan kesana.</font>

632
00:52:09,270 --> 00:52:11,330
<font color="yellow">Terima kasih.</font>

633
00:52:40,460 --> 00:52:41,460
<font color="yellow">Bibi.</font>

634
00:52:43,300 --> 00:52:47,820
<font color="yellow">Omo, Soon Young
ada apa kemari?</font>

635
00:52:47,820 --> 00:52:49,400
<font color="yellow">Lama tidak jumpa.</font>

636
00:52:50,860 --> 00:52:52,930
<font color="yellow">Senang bertemu denganmu.</font>

637
00:52:53,660 --> 00:52:54,730
<font color="yellow">Uang?</font>

638
00:53:09,630 --> 00:53:13,100
<font color="yellow">Setidaknya ini berharga
30 juta won.</font>

639
00:53:17,830 --> 00:53:18,900
<font color="yellow">Yang ini tidak.</font>

640
00:53:20,160 --> 00:53:22,830
<font color="yellow">Berikan saja 20 juta won.</font>

641
00:53:34,630 --> 00:53:35,800
<font color="yellow">Tulis nomor rekeningmu.</font>

642
00:53:36,160 --> 00:53:39,160
<font color="yellow">Tunai saja, Bibi tidak keberatan
tarik tunai?</font>

643
00:53:43,400 --> 00:53:46,460
<font color="yellow">Aku lupa nomor rekeningku.</font>

644
00:53:47,460 --> 00:53:49,060
<font color="yellow">Tunggu 10 menit.</font>

645
00:53:51,460 --> 00:53:53,930
<font color="yellow">Tidak harus uangnya Yeong Won, 'kan?</font>

646
00:53:54,830 --> 00:53:56,060
<font color="yellow">Kau tak mau uangku?</font>

647
00:53:57,160 --> 00:53:58,850
<font color="yellow">Bibi, aku...</font>

648
00:53:58,850 --> 00:54:00,190
<font color="yellow">Ambil lagi itu.</font>

649
00:54:00,190 --> 00:54:01,930
<font color="yellow">Aku tak ingin terbebani.</font>

650
00:54:05,400 --> 00:54:07,060
<font color="yellow">Baiklah, tinggalkan disitu.</font>

651
00:54:09,560 --> 00:54:10,560
<font color="yellow">Ayo.</font>

652
00:54:15,260 --> 00:54:18,490
<font color="yellow">Ada apa?/
Jangan beritahu Joeng A unni.</font>

653
00:54:18,490 --> 00:54:21,220
<font color="yellow">Semua anak wanita suka
buat masalah.</font>

654
00:54:21,220 --> 00:54:23,090
<font color="yellow">Putri siapa lagi yang
buat masalah?</font>

655
00:54:23,090 --> 00:54:26,440
<font color="yellow">Wan, anaknya Nan Hee.
Dia pacaran dengan pria beristri.</font>

656
00:54:26,440 --> 00:54:28,800
<font color="yellow">Jangan pura-pura tidak tahu.</font>

657
00:54:28,800 --> 00:54:30,530
<font color="yellow">Benar juga, kau 'kan artis.</font>

658
00:54:31,230 --> 00:54:32,440
<font color="yellow">Cih.</font>

659
00:54:32,440 --> 00:54:36,260
<font color="yellow">Coba tebak, Seong Jae Oppa muncul.</font>

660
00:54:48,560 --> 00:54:49,910
<font color="yellow">Ini laporannya.</font>

661
00:54:49,910 --> 00:54:51,850
<font color="yellow">Baik.</font>

662
00:54:51,850 --> 00:54:54,600
<font color="yellow">Berikan padaku kalau sudah selesai./
Iya, sebentar.</font>

663
00:55:01,930 --> 00:55:05,020
<font color="yellow">Kau sepertinya tidak bisa
fokus di rumah atau di kantor.</font>

664
00:55:05,020 --> 00:55:07,800
<font color="yellow">Kau harus kerja dimana?/
Yoo Jung.</font>

665
00:55:14,300 --> 00:55:16,210
<font color="yellow"><i>Dimana kalian?</i></font>

666
00:55:16,210 --> 00:55:20,360
<font color="yellow"><i>Persimpangan Hyeonchon.
Bukan, persimpangan Osam.</i></font>

667
