00:55:54,530 --> 00:55:56,300
<font color="yellow"><i>[Tabrak lari di persimpangan Hyeonchon]</i></font>

671
00:55:59,630 --> 00:56:03,060
<font color="yellow"><i>[Polisi Yongin mencari saksi mata
kasus tabrak lari tanggal 19]</i></font>

672
00:56:08,230 --> 00:56:11,260
<font color="yellow">Untuk judul sebaiknya...</font>

673
00:56:33,600 --> 00:56:35,630
<font color="yellow"><i>[Dicari saksi mata tabrak lari
tanggal 19]</i></font>

674
00:57:46,060 --> 00:57:47,900
<font color="yellow">Untung saja...</font>

675
00:57:49,360 --> 00:57:51,700
<font color="yellow">...yang tertabrak disana orang tua.</font>

676
00:57:56,000 --> 00:57:59,230
<font color="yellow">Untung bukan remaja
atau anak kecil.</font>

677
00:58:04,760 --> 00:58:07,460
<font color="yellow">Bibi, ayo kita minum teh.</font>

678
00:58:09,930 --> 00:58:11,130
<font color="yellow">Tidak mau.</font>

679
00:58:12,160 --> 00:58:15,430
<font color="yellow">Ikut saja. Aku harus minum
teh dengan Bibi.</font>

680
00:58:15,860 --> 00:58:17,240
<font color="yellow">Lain kali saja.</font>

681
00:58:17,240 --> 00:58:19,750
<font color="yellow">Bibi, ini salah.</font>

682
00:58:19,750 --> 00:58:21,950
<font color="yellow">Menurutku ini tidak benar.</font>

683
00:58:21,950 --> 00:58:23,930
<font color="yellow">Seseorang baru.../
Wan.</font>

684
00:58:28,460 --> 00:58:29,730
<font color="yellow">Diamlah.</font>

685
00:59:18,300 --> 00:59:21,060
<font color="yellow">Sedang apa kau?
Cepat masuk.</font>

686
00:59:26,330 --> 00:59:28,800
<font color="yellow">Jeong A! Aku lapar!</font>

687
00:59:30,330 --> 00:59:31,500
<font color="yellow">Kau mau kemana?</font>

688
00:59:39,700 --> 00:59:41,660
<font color="yellow">Kenapa klakson terus?</font>

689
00:59:45,160 --> 00:59:46,660
<font color="yellow">Terserah aku, kenapa?</font>

690
00:59:47,330 --> 00:59:48,600
<font color="yellow">Brengsek.</font>

691
00:59:49,930 --> 00:59:52,170
<font color="yellow">Mereka semua sudah gila.</font>

692
00:59:52,170 --> 00:59:54,030
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana kalau mereka tak
menyerahkan diri?</font>

693
00:59:54,660 --> 00:59:56,000
<font color="yellow">Apa yang akan terjadi?</font>

694
00:59:56,530 --> 00:59:58,000
<font color="yellow">Terserah mereka sajalah.</font>

695
00:59:58,330 --> 01:00:01,460
<font color="yellow">Banyak yang perlu
kukhawatirkan.</font>

696
01:00:01,830 --> 01:00:03,300
<font color="yellow">Suka-suka kalian saja.</font>

697
01:00:08,460 --> 01:00:10,960
<font color="yellow">Lagipula mereka takkan hidup
selamanya.</font>

698
01:00:11,760 --> 01:00:13,730
<font color="yellow">Tidak tahu malu.</font>

699
01:00:14,730 --> 01:00:17,610
<font color="yellow"><i>Saat aku memaki mereka...,</i></font>

700
01:00:17,610 --> 01:00:19,560
<font color="yellow"><i>...mereka memutuskan untuk
menyerahkan diri.</i></font>

701
01:00:20,660 --> 01:00:22,030
<font color="yellow">Kau juga.</font>

702
01:00:23,000 --> 01:00:24,460
<font color="yellow">Aku saja sendiri.</font>

703
01:00:28,260 --> 01:00:32,160
<font color="yellow">Baiklah, kita akan selalu bersama.</font>

704
01:00:33,400 --> 01:00:36,660
<font color="yellow">Aku segera kesana.</font>

705
01:00:37,130 --> 01:00:38,430
<font color="yellow">Tunggu aku ya.</font>

706
01:00:44,960 --> 01:00:47,800
<font color="yellow"><i>Bibi Hee Ja bilang....</i></font>

707
01:00:47,800 --> 01:00:49,500
<font color="yellow"><i>...tak ada lagi yang perlu dia urus.</i></font>

708
01:01:17,030 --> 01:01:20,830
<font color="yellow"><i>Awalnya, Bibi Jeong A tak
berencana menyerahkan diri.</i></font>

709
01:01:21,860 --> 01:01:24,530
<font color="yellow"><i>Apa salahnya menabrak orang tua
yang sudah bau tanah?</i></font>

710
01:01:24,930 --> 01:01:26,300
<font color="yellow"><i>Buat apa dipermasalahkan?</i></font>

711
01:01:27,360 --> 01:01:30,130
<font color="yellow"><i>Dia punya anak yang berhati dingin
dan suami keras kepala.</i></font>

712
01:01:31,160 --> 01:01:33,290
<font color="yellow"><i>Sebentar lagi ibunya juga akan mati.</i></font>

713
01:01:33,290 --> 01:01:35,660
<font color="yellow"><i>Dia pikir dialah yang
harus dikasihani.</i></font>

714
01:01:36,130 --> 01:01:37,660
<font color="yellow"><i>Begitulah yang dia pikirkan.</i></font>

715
01:01:39,030 --> 01:01:41,500
<font color="yellow"><i>Tapi saat di mobil bersamaku...,</i></font>

716
01:01:42,660 --> 01:01:46,230
<font color="yellow"><i>...Bibi melihat bayangannya di cermin
dan menyadari sesuatu.</i></font>

717
01:01:49,630 --> 01:01:51,030
<font color="yellow"><i>Aku juga sudah tua. </i></font>

718
01:01:51,930 --> 01:01:53,800
<font color="yellow"><i>Apa itu artinya...</i></font>

719
01:01:54,330 --> 01:01:56,860
<font color="yellow"><i>...aku pantas mati di jalan seperti dia?</i></font>

720
01:01:58,260 --> 01:02:00,160
<font color="yellow"><i>Hatinya berkata tidak.</i></font>

721
01:02:00,860 --> 01:02:03,330
<font color="yellow"><i>Saat itulah dia menyadari perbuatannya...,</i></font>

722
01:02:03,830 --> 01:02:06,700
<font color="yellow"><i>...dan penyesalan mulai muncul.</i></font>

723
01:02:31,130 --> 01:02:32,460
<font color="yellow">Syalnya bagus.</font>

724
01:02:39,700 --> 01:02:40,930
<font color="yellow">Pakai saja.</font>

725
01:02:41,400 --> 01:02:42,400
<font color="yellow">Untukmu saja.</font>

726
01:02:50,500 --> 01:02:54,660
<font color="yellow">Nanti di kantor polisi, bilang
saja aku pelakunya.</font>

727
01:02:55,860 --> 01:02:58,250
<font color="yellow">Aku tak punya apa-apa lagi.</font>

728
01:02:58,250 --> 01:02:59,630
<font color="yellow">Aku ini janda.</font>

729
01:03:10,630 --> 01:03:13,400
<font color="yellow">Bisa kami pesan dua cangkir teh?/
Baik.</font>

730
01:03:25,200 --> 01:03:26,430
<font color="yellow">Hubungi Wan.</font>

731
01:03:27,600 --> 01:03:28,600
<font color="yellow">Iya.</font>

732
01:03:30,260 --> 01:03:33,090
<font color="yellow"><i>Mereka bilang sebelum
ke kantor polisi...,</i></font>

733
01:03:33,090 --> 01:03:35,930
<font color="yellow"><i>...mereka ingin menikmati teh panas
selama mungkin...</i></font>

734
01:03:35,930 --> 01:03:38,600
<font color="yellow"><i>...untuk menghangatkan hidup
mereka yang menyedihkan.</i></font>

735
01:03:56,200 --> 01:03:57,260
<font color="yellow">Apa-apaan ini?</font>

736
01:04:00,130 --> 01:04:01,130
<font color="yellow">Taksi.</font>

737
01:04:01,700 --> 01:04:02,900
<font color="yellow">Taksi.</font>

738
01:04:03,700 --> 01:04:06,830
<font color="yellow"><i>Wan. Ini Bibi Jeong A dan Bibi Hee Ja.</i></font>

739
01:04:07,630 --> 01:04:10,000
<font color="yellow"><i>Kami mau ke kantor polisi.</i></font>

740
01:04:10,860 --> 01:04:12,860
<font color="yellow"><i>Terima kasih, Wan.</i></font>

741
01:04:13,330 --> 01:04:15,630
<font color="yellow"><i>Kami minta maaf.</i></font>

742
01:04:16,030 --> 01:04:17,500
<font color="yellow"><i>Semoga kau bahagia.</i></font>

743
01:04:19,730 --> 01:04:22,040
<font color="yellow"><i>Apanya yang menakutkan?</i></font>

744
01:04:22,040 --> 01:04:24,960
<font color="yellow"><i>Aksi bunuh diri itu cuma pura-pura saja?</i></font>

745
01:04:25,700 --> 01:04:28,090
<font color="yellow"><i>Bibi punya anak, 'kan?</i></font>

746
01:04:28,090 --> 01:04:29,570
<font color="yellow"><i>Aku bukan anaknya Bibi.</i></font>

747
01:04:29,570 --> 01:04:32,250
<font color="yellow"><i>Kenapa selalu minta tolong padaku?</i></font>

748
01:04:32,250 --> 01:04:34,980
<font color="yellow"><i>Aku juga sibuk. Aku tidak
selalu punya waktu luang.</i></font>

749
01:04:34,980 --> 01:04:36,800
<font color="yellow"><i>Tolong hentikan.</i></font>

750
01:04:37,260 --> 01:04:39,990
<font color="yellow"><i>Orang tua seharusnya
duduk di rumah.</i></font>

751
01:04:39,990 --> 01:04:43,260
<font color="yellow"><i>Kenapa keluar segala?</i></font>

752
01:04:44,030 --> 01:04:47,300
<font color="yellow"><i>Kalau aku seumuran kalian, mati
sekarang pun tak masalah.</i></font>

753
01:04:48,330 --> 01:04:50,570
<font color="yellow"><i>Mereka semua sudah gila.</i></font>

754
01:04:50,570 --> 01:04:52,230
<font color="yellow"><i>Bagaimana jika mereka tak menyerahkan diri?</i></font>

755
01:04:52,700 --> 01:04:54,000
<font color="yellow"><i>Apa yang akan terjadi?</i></font>

756
01:04:54,330 --> 01:04:56,860
<font color="yellow"><i>Lagipula mereka takkan hidup
selamanya.</i></font>

757
01:04:57,660 --> 01:04:59,330
<font color="yellow"><i>Dasar tak tahu malu.</i></font>

758
01:05:00,560 --> 01:05:02,430
<font color="yellow"><i>Mereka bukannya tak tahu malu.</i></font>

759
01:05:03,060 --> 01:05:06,500
<font color="yellow"><i>Mereka sudah menderita
