763
01:05:16,460 --> 01:05:18,040
<font color="yellow">Halo, Wan.</font>

764
01:05:18,040 --> 01:05:21,360
<font color="yellow">Bibi. Bibi dimana?</font>

765
01:05:21,860 --> 01:05:25,360
<font color="yellow">Kafe mana? Bibi, kita bertemu dulu.</font>

766
01:05:26,200 --> 01:05:28,830
<font color="yellow">Baiklah, tolong tunggu aku.</font>

767
01:05:29,230 --> 01:05:32,030
<font color="yellow">Di kafe mana?</font>

768
01:05:34,000 --> 01:05:35,030
<font color="yellow">Bibi.</font>

769
01:06:15,260 --> 01:06:18,130
<font color="yellow"><i>Jika aku disana bersama mereka,
bukannya teh yang kami minum...</i></font>

770
01:06:18,670 --> 01:06:20,800
<font color="yellow"><i>...aku akan pesan
anggur untuk Bibi Hee Ja...</i></font>

771
01:06:21,230 --> 01:06:25,000
<font color="yellow"><i>...dan bir hitam pahit untuk
